sentences.en_translation: I was born and raised in Sierra Leone, a small and very beautiful country in West Africa, rich in both natural resources and creative talent.

sentences.sentence: Kuomet aš, būdamas 12, ir mano šeima bėgome gelbėdamiesi nuo užpuolikų, nusprendžiau, kad padarysiu viską, kad mano vaikams netektų patirti to, ką teko patirti man.
sentences.en_translation: When I, at the age of 12, and my family ran to escape the attackers, I decided to do my best to keep my children from experiencing what I had to experience.

sentences.sentence: Aš tikiuosi ir trokštu, kad įrankiai ir procesai kuriami mūsų tyrėjų padės sukurti labai funkcionalius protezus tiems, kuriems jų reikia.

sentences.en_translation: I believe that the souls of people who have experienced war and disease begin to heal when the convenient and affordable interfaces needed for their bodies are created.
